<div>
    <h1>MarketPlace</h1>
<dl>
    <dd>Marketplace is  a platform for people who wants to buy or sell  new/used products
Users who wants to buy any product can explore the list of products according to the 
category and prices and they can also find the seller details on the website
In the same way, the users who wants to sell their product can post the 
advertisement of the product they want to sell by adding the relevant information of 
the product
    </dd>
</dl>


<form action="product/exploreproduct" method="get">
<input type="submit" value="Explore Products" />
</form>
<form action="product/advertisement" method="get">
<input type="submit" value="Post an advertisement" />
</form>
<p>{{error}}</p>
</div>

{{#if user}}
<p><a href="/logout"  id="Log-out" >Log Out</a></p>
{{else}}
<div id="form"  >

<h2>Login here</h2>

<div class="form-elem" >
  <form method="POST" id="login-form" action="/login" >
    
      <label for="email">email.:</label>
      <input
        name="email"
        id="email"
        type="text"
        value="{{email}}"
        placeholder="email"
      />
    
      <label for="password">Password:</label>
      <input
        name="password"
        id="password"
        type="password"
        placeholder="password(6 - characters minimum)"
      />
    </div>
    <button type="submit">Login</button>
    <a href="/signup" class="carrd-link">Need to register? Click here to sign-up</a>
  </form>
</div>
